node.text: Check out all of the pipes and mugs I will have in my shop update tomorrow! Also get some inside scoop on how to check out faster in order to get the pipe that you love!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Diverse Earth Studios on August 19, 2021.

node.text:
Wow! What a wonderful shop restock! 🥰🙏💕
You all continue to humble me with your love and support! 😭
I'm grateful everyday to live this creative lifestyle! 💜
There are still a handful of gorgeous pieces in my shop as well as a few pre-order designs! 
💕
Head over to the link in my bio to check them out!💜💜💜
I'll be shipping all orders tomorrow. 💜 Much love to you all, wishing you a great Thursday!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Diverse Earth Studios on August 19, 2021.
Photo by Diverse Earth Studios on August 19, 2021.
Photo by Diverse Earth Studios on August 18, 2021.

node.text:
Today is the day! Finally!😅
All of these juicy wares will be live at 9pm EST tonight! 
💦🍓🍄🦋🌙✨
Everything is on my site for preview with prices. I also have 3 designs for pre-order. 💙
💕💕
Don't forget your hard case! You can even add it to your cart now so don't have to worry about it while trying to snag a piece. 
💕💕
Much love to everyone showing me love this past week. 🥰😭🙏💕

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Diverse Earth Studios on August 17, 2021. May be an image of jewelry.

node.text:
Gah! It's almost here! Restock day is tomorrow! 😅💜
Do you have your reminders set? 🕘⏰
I just added some pre-order listing to my site as well! 🍄🦋🌿
Do you have your eyes on something in particular? 💕

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Diverse Earth Studios on August 16, 2021.

node.text:
Mushrooms all around! 🍄 Which shroomy is calling you?💙
Available this Wednesday 8/18 @ 9pm EST. 
Previews are up on my website. Link in bio.💕

Wait for it! Yaas!😍🦋 I'm so in love with this batch I can't even!😭💜

💜💗

node.text:
Introducing the: "Please leave me a review Giveaway" 🥰💕🙏
As a huge thank you to all of my customers I'll be giving away a strawberry rose quartz heart pipe along with the Diverse Earth Studios hard carrying case! This giveaway is only open to previous customers. 💕
✨
I am where I am today because of yalls' continued support of my artwork. I can't put into words how grateful I am to live this life!!🙏😭💕 
🍓
I would be delighted if you would leave a review on my website. (Please email me if you had an issue with your order. I would love to make it right!)
🍓
Here are the Diverse Earth Studios giveaway guidelines:
✨
🍓Look for an email from me (diverseearthstudios.@gmail.com) with a link to leave a review. Leave a review.💕
🍓Like and save this post
🍓Leave a few favorite emoji as a comment.
🍓 If you don't see my email please email me and I'll send a link. 
🍓Must be of legal age to smoke🚭 in your state to participate.
✨
💎I will choose a winner in a few days.
💎 Feel free to sign up for my email list to get important info on the shop restock. (Link in bio)
💎I only send emails a couple times a month so you won't be bombarded.
💎Feel free to share any of my work on your feed or stories for extra entries.
💎This giveaway is only open to the US.
✨
🚨🚨🚨Do not engage with anyone (pretending to be me) messaging you saying you won the giveaway. This is my ONLY account. 🚨🚨🚨 
This Instagram giveaway is not sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with Instagram.
